{"type":"question","id":24504,"title":"豆瓣贴主为买房，每月献血小板两次，能增收400元。怎么评价？","uid":21875,"topics":[26,4887,2239,163,759],"contents":"【现实版的许三观卖血记】<br>\n<br>\n在豆瓣看到一个帖子，为了攒钱买房，贴主一个月献血小板两次。（说是献血，其实就是卖血。）<br>\n<br>\n一个月献血小板两次，一次200元，能增收400元。<br>\n<br>\n这位贴主总计已经献血超过1万毫升。大家怎么看？<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/yqLJuM4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yqLJuM4.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/yqLJuM4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/zrBVyAY.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zrBVyAY.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/zrBVyAY.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/3OTAbt6.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3OTAbt6.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/3OTAbt6.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-04-29","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":5}